Firstly: thank you this will be such a helpful feature.
Second: I'm getting the error "Copy to HubL failed" sporadically - I have a feeling the common denominator has to do with when a custom module is present in the copied section (just a hunch tho)
Has anyone else experienced this? Is there a solution?

<@UFL9XN2DQ> I don’t have any issues with custom modules being copied in the section. Wonder if maybe there is an error in one of the modules? If youre still seeing this error it’s likely that if you pop open the console there will prob be an error of some kind showing up in there in the page editor.
